<h2>Absence Reminder</h2>
<p>Dear <%= user.email %>,</p>
<p>We regret to inform you that you were marked as absent for your venue booking as you did not present on time.</p>
<p>Please be reminded to attend all booked timeslots punctually.</p>
<p>Here are your booking details:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Venue:</strong> <%= venue_record.venue.name %></li>
  <li><strong>Building:</strong> <%= venue_record.venue.building %></li>
  <li><strong>Date:</strong> <%= venue_record.date %></li>
  <li><strong>Time:</strong> <%= venue_record.time.strftime("%H:%M") %></li>
</ul>
<p>If you have any questions, please contact support.</p>